---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Tony Ingram, PhD - Personal website of Tony Ingram, PhD"
  description="Personal website of Tony Ingram, PhD."
  canonicalPath="/"
>
  <section class="section hero">
    <div class="site-shell hero__inner">
      <img
        class="hero__image"
        src="/images/tonyingram_phd_crop.jpg"
        alt="Tony Ingram, PhD"
        width="1163"
        height="1162"
      />
      <div class="hero__copy">
        <h1>Aligning brains, bodies, and tech.</h1>
      <p>
          Clinician (MSc PT) → neuroscientist (PhD) → neurotech founder → AI product manager. I
          thrive in deeply technical projects, aligning teams to deliver results.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="site-shell narrow-shell prose-block">
      <h2 class="section-heading section-heading--center">About Tony</h2>
      <p>
        I dream big, but execute with rigour and respect for reality. I&apos;ve dedicated my career
        to studying neuroscience and applying it in the real world. It&apos;s going to take a while,
        but I believe that neurotechnology will be the most important technology of this century
        &ndash; but for now, it&apos;s AI.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently, I am an AI product leader driving enhancements in a multi-million-dollar drug
        discovery product used by top global pharmaceutical companies. Previously, I founded and
        led a neurotechnology startup from concept through to clinical pilots at leading
        institutions, raising millions in financing. The startup was founded during my PhD in
        Neuroscience, and before that I was a licensed healthcare professional specializing in
        neurorehabilitation. During my studies, I ran award-winning youth-outreach dance
        companies.
      </p>
      <p>
        I&apos;ve worked in hospitals, academia, startups, and global enterprise. This broad
        experience has made me a cross-functional leader who can bridge academic science, deep
        technology development, and commercial strategy, while staying grounded in the human side
        of work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="site-shell narrow-shell follow-section">
      <h2 class="section-heading section-heading--center">Follow my journey</h2>
      <ul class="follow-list">
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tgjingram/">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
              <path
                d="M100.28 448H7.4V148.9h92.88zM53.79 108.1C24.09 108.1 0 83.5 0 53.8a53.79 53.79 0 0 1 107.58 0c0 29.7-24.1 54.3-53.79 54.3zM447.9 448h-92.68V302.4c0-34.7-.7-79.2-48.29-79.2-48.29 0-55.69 37.7-55.69 76.7V448h-92.78V148.9h89.08v40.8h1.3c12.4-23.5 42.69-48.3 87.88-48.3 94 0 111.28 61.9 111.28 142.3V448z"
              />
            </svg>
            <span>Career</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/toniolio">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 496 512">
              <path
                d="M165.9 397.4c0 2-2.3 3.6-5.2 3.6-3.3.3-5.6-1.3-5.6-3.6 0-2 2.3-3.6 5.2-3.6 3-.3 5.6 1.3 5.6 3.6zm-31.1-4.5c-.7 2 1.3 4.3 4.3 4.9 2.6 1 5.6 0 6.2-2s-1.3-4.3-4.3-5.2c-2.6-.7-5.5.3-6.2 2.3zm44.2-1.7c-2.9.7-4.9 2.6-4.6 4.9.3 2 2.9 3.3 5.9 2.6 2.9-.7 4.9-2.6 4.6-4.6-.3-1.9-3-3.2-5.9-2.9zM244.8 8C106.1 8 0 113.3 0 252c0 110.9 69.8 205.8 169.5 239.2 12.8 2.3 17.3-5.6 17.3-12.1 0-6.2-.3-40.4-.3-61.4 0 0-70 15-84.7-29.8 0 0-11.4-29.1-27.8-36.6 0 0-22.9-15.7 1.6-15.4 0 0 24.9 2 38.6 25.8 21.9 38.6 58.6 27.5 72.9 20.9 2.3-16 8.8-27.1 16-33.7-55.9-6.2-112.3-14.3-112.3-110.5 0-27.5 7.6-41.3 23.6-58.9-2.6-6.5-11.1-33.3 2.6-67.9 20.9-6.5 69 27 69 27 20-5.6 41.5-8.5 62.8-8.5s42.8 2.9 62.8 8.5c0 0 48.1-33.6 69-27 13.7 34.7 5.2 61.4 2.6 67.9 16 17.7 25.8 31.5 25.8 58.9 0 96.5-58.9 104.2-114.8 110.5 9.2 7.9 17 22.9 17 46.4 0 33.7-.3 75.4-.3 83.6 0 6.5 4.6 14.4 17.3 12.1C428.2 457.8 496 362.9 496 252 496 113.3 383.5 8 244.8 8z"
              />
            </svg>
            <span>Code</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/143038589">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 384 512">
              <path
                d="M158.4 0L7 292h89.2l62.2-116.1L220.1 292h88.5zm150.2 292l-43.9 88.2-44.6-88.2h-67.6l112.2 220 111.5-220z"
              />
